  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An abandoned school. Silenced screams.</strong><br>Oblivion is a short first-person horror/thriller experience focused on storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players take on the role of detective <strong>Lucas Peralta</strong>, sent to investigate a mysterious case at a forgotten school.<br>But within those walls, silence isn’t the only thing that lingers—echoes of the past still whisper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Only those who remember, suffer.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to remember?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An abandoned school. Silenced screams.</strong><br>Oblivion is a short first-person horror/thriller experience focused on storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players take on the role of detective <strong>Lucas Peralta</strong>, sent to investigate a mysterious case at a forgotten school.<br>But within those walls, silence isn’t the only thing that lingers—echoes of the past still whisper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Only those who remember, suffer.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to remember?</p>",
